    <h1>MODEL QUESTION PAPER FOR SUMMATIVE TEST-II</h1>
    <h2>MATHEMATICS</h2>
    <h2>CLASS-VIII</h2>

    <p><strong>Maximum Marks:</strong> 20</p>

    <p class="instructions"><strong>General Instructions:</strong></p>
    <ol>
        <li>All questions are compulsory.</li>
        <li>The question paper consists of 7 questions divided into 2 sections A and B.</li>
        <li>Section A contains 4 questions of 2 marks each.</li>
        <li>Section B contains 3 questions of 4 marks each.</li>
    </ol>

    <p class="section">SECTION A</p>

    <p><strong>Q1:</strong> What will be the product of \( (a^2) \times (2a^{22}) \times (4a^{26}) \) ?</p>
    <ul>
        <li>(a) 8a<sup>46</sup></li>
        <li>(b) 8a<sup>48</sup></li>
        <li>(c) 6a<sup>30</sup></li>
        <li>(d) 8a<sup>50</sup></li>
    </ul>

    <p><strong>Q2:</strong> Water is oxidized to oxygen by</p>
    <ul>
        <li>(a) H<sub>2</sub>O<sub>2</sub></li>
        <li>(b) KMnO<sub>4</sub></li>
        <li>(c) ClO<sub>2</sub></li>
        <li>(d) Fluorine</li>
    </ul>

    <p><strong>Note:</strong> Cutting is not allowed. Select only one option.</p>

